Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.89,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it was around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:17.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:17.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu(overlap),0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:17.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin(overlap),0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No fair, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:20.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have to say that, too, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:21.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt like it, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:22.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:24.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What type of joke was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:28.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:39.31,Kanojo_Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}If {\c&H53AC43&}Her {\c&H085DF0&}Flag {\c&HD2C345&}Breaks
