Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.97,Kanojo_Flag_Ep_Title,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(730,1)}Believe {\c&HDAB776&}and Wait for Me. \N{\c&H9650D9&}I'm not {\c&H3DB6E7&}Going to be Late{\c&H5DBC91&} for My Date {\c&HD1C35E&}With Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:06.01,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,So can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:07.56,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.23,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:13.48,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to go out somewhere \Nwith you, even if only just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.64,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, that shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:25.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you did say okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:25.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you kept a secret like that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:30.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,from your sister, Sou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:32.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a thieving cat, a homewrecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Cats are cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:41.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We can all just accompany him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Akane wasn't the only one who put \Nin long hours for the track meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:52.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,That means you should come \Nwith us, too, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:59.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you were able to include \Nyourself as part of the date today
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,just like that, Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:02.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want this at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:09.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now we're going to decide who \Ngets to be with Souta-kun first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:20.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We've figured out who's going when. \NHurry up and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:23.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have to say that twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri isn't going, either, supposedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,She's looking into something, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's that, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I guess I'll go have fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, I may be staying here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't need to get me \Nanything while you're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:56.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Especially these limited-time only cakes. \NI don't need them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need them at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying everything twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I guess I'm a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:17.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be a man today \Nand escort you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's pulling her boyfriend everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice to be on a first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:34.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Souta always finds a way into trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,and Akane and the others are \Nalways doing something silly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but they're all gone today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the queen of the Quest Dorm right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:43.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this and no one can stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't get it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is harder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.44,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I began to see flags,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.24,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,not only on on humans, but on other things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.76,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something at Quest Dorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Megumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:59.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:05.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:09.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,We should go someplace you \Nwant to next, as thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, what do I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess I'm kind of hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Then I know a good place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:22.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's very manly, with extra-large portions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu, what's this supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:34.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a super-special parfait \Nthat no one has ever finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Now show off your manliness and eat it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:50.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think this is going \Nto work, man or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so full...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:01.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so full?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:11.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship is when you \Nfight your battles together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There's some cream on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:31.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, a little more to your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:33.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez... Get it for me, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.68,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone here an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.76,yakisoba_08:09,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakisoba
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:23.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No. I've been waiting \Nfor you all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:24.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You waited that long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:27.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's Akane's turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:34.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time going \Nsomewhere with a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:39.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,so I asked my father and mother what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Asked them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:44.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,My father told me this place would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:45.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is surprisingly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:55.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,My father said that any couple \Nthat got on these boats
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,would definitely break up, \Nso they're perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:06.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:10.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We're not a couple, so I don't \Nsuspect there will be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:14.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, since we're not a couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,then we'll never leave each other's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:23.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'd like for us \Nto be a couple someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:34.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,T-Time for me to show you my \Nauthentic Italian boating skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Paddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:40.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Paddle. Paddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll concede that was impressive, \Nbut something seems off here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You mean like we're in the wrong \Ntimezone and I'm Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:46.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you could say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:49.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's paddle together. \NYeah, that's best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You mean we get to work \Ntogether, the two of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:56.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if I do something weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:01.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take one paddle, \Nand you get the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:13.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:24.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:49.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,M-My mom told me to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,wear my good underwear, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.83,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What is your mom teaching you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do good? Did I do bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! We just need to \Nget your clothes dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we should go somewhere \Nwhere there won't be any people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:06.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fun by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can eat and sleep as much as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There really isn't anyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:20.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:23.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Not many people come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:27.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I got to be such \Ngood friends with her so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Is this where...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:33.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to come here with you at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:37.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Not too long ago I couldn't \Neven come close to here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,but now I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:44.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You said that nothing can happen to me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,until I see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:49.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't run into her again yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:52.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,but I did meet you, \Nand have become close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:54.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:57.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to thank both of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,you and her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should be the one saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,S-Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rin-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku made me wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:30.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I bet this frilly stuff \Ndoesn't look good on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I know you think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.15,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A yandere flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.91,cleared_12:46,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Cleared
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:53.39,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's too easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's great how quiet it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:00.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I wish it was this quiet all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:05.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I could \Njust sit back like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:08.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,It's been kind of busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:12.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's do something tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:15.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at them brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:23.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I forgot I have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:28.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So you brought these for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:35.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Every day was so much fun back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:38.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I wish life could've stayed that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Souta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having tons of fun right now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:45.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-kun, you remember this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:54.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,That was when we took on the \Nbathhouse's chimney and won.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:56.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.05,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:01.01,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm glad we made it \Nto the top before I moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:07.70,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,S-Souta... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.48,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, to commemorate this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.96,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I say we have a pissing contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:14.08,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.58,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What? You scared of losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.28,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. You're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.71,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,On your mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:31.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rin-kun, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:35.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know we were kids, b-but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:38.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,All right! You're a man, take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Responsibility for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:43.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You know exactly what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:47.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:50.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey— Rin-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okiku-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:00.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-ku—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:12.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You all want to go somewhere with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:18.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can go with you if you really insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:20.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:27.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan'll be fine once she gets a little rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:38.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There might not be enough time \Nto go somewhere with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:45.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:50.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,If you're really upset about it, \Nthen sleep on my lap for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Normally it's the guy who asks that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:58.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I really like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-nee, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:07.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:10.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:21.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Okiku-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:23.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.04,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.91,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,But now I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.57,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.21,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:44.85,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is important to me, \Nand I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.33,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,And... And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:53.04,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... I'll be your little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.46,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.46,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be your little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.56,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:03.89,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.79,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:07.39,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.85,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you call me "oneechan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:11.67,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.16,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:15.80,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I haven't been that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:25.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I really haven't be a good little \Nbrother character for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you, you're not \Na "little brother character,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,you're actually my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:37.49,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My real sister got mad at me for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.72,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,being someone else's little brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:44.00,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but both of them are important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.38,women_17:45,,0000,0000,0000,,Women
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I had a great day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I had Quest Dorm all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:03.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was bad of us to go off
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and have fun without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:07.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:11.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You let us have your time with Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed by your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.20,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing how far Souta's come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:30.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought he'd be going on dates \Nwith girls on his days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:32.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You guys haven't forgotten, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:42.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You know, don't you? \NSouta told you all, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:45.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,While I was watching \Nthe house, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,We know... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:55.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Souta and all of you suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I guess I was hearing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:04.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I have a report on the \Nunderground passageway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:09.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:15.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I have concluded that the passageway exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,However, according to my ground scans,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,it seems the passageway was buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:22.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,So I... dug it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:34.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't call myself an android \Nif I didn't have a drill or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You have everything, don't you, Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:48.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the First Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:54.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The truth of the world might be... \Nbehind this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:16.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Knight, magician,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,bishop, ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The same as the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:23.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really recognize the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot scan the interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:27.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be made of a special material.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:31.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we can't solve the mystery that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:33.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just leave it here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:41.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's head back for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:42.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:45.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So what's over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:46.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,The outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:50.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I've confirmed it connects to \Nthe forest behind Quest Dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's this light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's being generated \Nby a large amount of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri, watch after the \Npeople in the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:16.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I think very highly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:19.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,of you messing with this world's flags,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:25.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Enormous Death Flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:12.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:15.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering for a while, \Nbut what's up with that roar thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:17.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's an official greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:17.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Official?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:20.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "roar," anyway. It's "gawo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.26,0:23:21.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The "wo" from "gawore."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:23.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,In English letters, it's "w-o."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:24.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A very detailed answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:26.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Now say it with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:27.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting up until you say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.68,0:23:29.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is the "teacher won't let you go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:30.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,home until you eat all your school lunch flag."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.85,0:23:31.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Roar. Gawo.
