Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:35.01,Kanojo_Flag_Next_Ep_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCAC65B&}Phew. {\c&H3ABBF9&}Don't {\c&H5ACC93&}scare me like that. {\c&H3CBAE6&}I guess {\c&HAA52E0&}you're just a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:32.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Too quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:34.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
